Patch Set 2:

> (1 comment)

Thanks for your review.I have view other files but do not find.I also view get_notification_transport method in oslo_messaging and think this (aliases) look like unused. :)

Patch Set 2:

It is actually used: https://github.com/openstack/oslo.messaging/blob/5690156d9b73e39547dbc3d27b12b41321bb6500/oslo_messaging/transport.py#L281

But it is depreated: https://github.com/openstack/oslo.messaging/blob/5690156d9b73e39547dbc3d27b12b41321bb6500/oslo_messaging/transport.py#L248

Some old configurations may contain old transport names, like 'glance.openstack.common.rpc.impl_kombu', which shoild be translated to 'rabbit'. Such configuration will not work without this aliases.

But I don't think that someone will update openstack but not update configuration.

But please update the commit message. This variable is not unused. It is deprecated.

Patch Set 2:

Ok,thanks for your advice. :)
